any 3rd party plug-ins installed?

From email:

No 3rd party plug-ins installed. To verify this, I just downloaded
Eclipse SDK 3.2M1 (latest milestone/stable) and did a fresh install. I
get the same error.

Found the problem. I had Unsanity`s ApplicationEnhancer and WindowShade 4
installed. Disabling both solved the problem.
